The red carpet was filled with eye-catching looks at the Brit Awards last night. The annual music event has seen a whole host of iconic fashion outfits over the years – from Geri Halliwell’s Union Jack dress to Kate Moss wearing David Bowie’s Ziggy Stardust playsuit. And stars certainly made an impression at London’s O2 Arena this year with sequins, latex, see-through gowns and more. Cut-out fashion and hooded dresses were a firm favourite on the red carpet for 2023, as well as black and gold ensembles. We’ve rounded up some of our favourite looks of the night. This article contains affiliate links. We will earn a small commission on purchases made through one of these links but this never influences our experts’ opinions. Products are tested and reviewed independently of commercial initiatives. Do you have a story to share? Get in touch by emailing MetroLifestyleTeam@Metro.co.uk. MORE : Ellie Goulding praises ‘gentleman’ Tom Grennan despite ‘inappropriate’ remark about her breasts at Brit Awards 2023 MORE : From Harry Styles’ triumph to Wet Leg’s anti-Tory dig and Sam Smith’s Unholy spectacle – Brit Awards 2023 standout moments